  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">\"Watching, Waiting,\" published by Leuven University Press in 2023, is a significant scholarly work reflecting contemporary themes. Despite the absence of citations or online mentions, the book's commercial presence on platforms like Amazon and Goodreads indicates a potential outreach to broader audiences.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">\"Watching, Waiting\" stands as an essential contribution to its field, published by Leuven University Press in 2023. While formal metrics such as citations, Wikipedia mentions, and community discussions on platforms like Reddit and Bluesky currently stand at zero, the book\u2019s availability on prominent commercial platforms like Amazon and Goodreads signals its accessibility to a broader readership beyond academia.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The commercial linkage indicates a possible interest from the public, which could pave the way for future discussions and potential integrates into community discourse. This lays the groundwork for the book to become a resource not only in scholarly discussions but also within wider societal contexts, especially as it engages with contemporary ideas that resonate with audiences beyond traditional academic circles.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Furthermore, the book encompasses themes relevant to sustainability and policy, reflected in an SDG indicator, fostering a discussion around its relevance to pressing global challenges. This aspect may enhance its academic impact as researchers and practitioners consider its insights in relation to sustainable development goals.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">In summary, while \"Watching, Waiting\" has yet to generate significant academic or community discourse, its strong commercial visibility and alignment with key global themes suggest potential for future impact. It has the capacity to influence both scholarly research and public understanding as it finds its place within ongoing conversations in its field.</p>",
